text: Ærest, feovertyne gearda beneoþan þam pytte, þanon of Collengaburnan west, up to þam hæþenan byrgelsan, þanon on scortan dyc.
Þonne to scealdan crundle, þanon to preostan lypan, þanon andlang grenan dene on þa foxholo westweard, þanon on Bradanbeorg, þonne on Blerianhylle.
Þanon on Wylberhtes stan, swa forth eall herpathes and dunes, þanon on Guþredesburg norþweard, þonne on Pendes clif, þanon on Blerianhylle, þanon on þa swelgende.
Þonne on iebyng crundele, þanon on Sceorran hlinc, þanon east to þara þreora æcera and heafdon, þanon to þan wylle on Collengaburnan.
